Class JSONHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ucl.msccs2016.om.gc99.JSONHandler

  • class JSONHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Primary Utility Class used to read/write JSON output using the Google Gson library; also used to clone objects using the same library.

    References & Libraries:
    Google - Gson User Guide. [Online]. Available: https://github.com/google/gson/blob/master/UserGuide.md
    Google - Gson Library. [Online]. Available: https://github.com/google/gson
